Changelog: WebUI 0.8 (beta-1)

##################################################################
#                          General                               #
##################################################################

- New features
- Bugfixes


##################################################################
#                          Library                               #
##################################################################

http://support.sibvisions.com
 
[NEW] 

  - #96:  user-defined condition for link cell editor
  - #266: registry support
  - #267: support for included search columns
  - #271: sort support for grid/table
  - #272: sort on Header option support 
  - #280: moved cellformatter handling to LinkTableCache
  - #281: checked size and precision for cell editors
  - send URL parameters to service (only during startup)
  - calculate WebTable size only once per event cycle
  - added force-reload option to WebTable
  - label foreground color set
  - default cell editors (number, date) configured and used
  - WebEditor noch checks readonly of databooks
  - GVxGrid: select previous row if an error occurs during row change
  - WebTable: refresh row after inserted
  - use nullable property for background of editor and table cells
  - discreet mask


[BUGFIX]

  - #252: window title not correct for downloaded files
  - #256: add Tabset does not work with our layouts
  - #258: set z-index to support modal frames
  - #264: Modality switch with negative location 
  - #265: readonly detection for editors
  - #270: Row index is wrong after grid sort 
  - #277: FormLayout wrong calculation with invisible components
  - dividerPosition and dividerAlignment in GVxSplitPanel mixed up
  - multiline editors supports ENTER (move to a new line instead
    of save)
  - IndexOutOfBoundsException in WebUI client
  - wrong preferred size calculation in TextAreas
  - default number format
  - endless loop with grid and editor